metadata.name: Little Island 🏝️
metadata.description:
🏝️🏝️ Little Island 🏝️🏝️

When we've had a life crisis, disappointment, sadness, or work stress, the things that make us feel better are just getting some rest, pausing your work, and traveling to a little warm and bright island where we can let go of our stress and listen to the sea and waves, recharging for a new day.

⛵️⛵️⛵️⛵️

This piece of work was inspired by the music box. When it’s playing, it makes me feel more relaxed and inspired.
